{
  "stem": "1929.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no reform movement that I'm sure there wasn't.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we were-- on the orthodox side-- we would have been probably the most enlightened.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think that's the word they used.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Enlightened.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We used to go to synagogue and everything like that, but-- well, you know, I just told you, my mother send us down-- she wouldn't tolerate having ham in the house, but outside of the house, I guess it was all right.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were not fanatical religious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And also, I think the big distinction in my family was that the children did not learn the Hebrew in the traditional way, which at that time, was going to an old Jewish Heider, it was called.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, where the-- there was usually one person that would teach these kids.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he would-- they-- you know, they-- and sometimes it could be quite brutal.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The man whipped them and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Not everyone, but, but this was the regular reputation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they would learn-- they would learn the prayers and the holy books and things like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because-- when I say-- a good example of my family being enlightened is the fact that my, my brothers and my sisters learned Hebrew as a language in the gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they all spoke Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were great Zionists.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Wow.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did they-- did they-- did you know any Hebrew when you were a child?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, the tragedy of it was that when my-- my turn never came to go to school, to the higher school.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I never learned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I would have wished they weren't so enlightened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would have learned more.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do remember one song.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Something about [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Something-- something about two little kittens.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
